quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  61,6,"And call to mind when Jesus, son of Mary, said: “O Children of Israel, I am Allah's Messenger to you, I verify the Torah which has come before me, and I give you the glad tiding of a Messenger who shall come after me, his name being Ahmad.” Yet when he came to them with Clear Signs they said: “This is sheer trickery.”"{1}{2}{3}{4},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2,footnotes:3:3,footnotes:4:4
  61,7,"Who would be more unjust than he who invents a lie about Allah the while he is being called to Islam? Allah does not direct such evildoing folk to the Right Way."{1}{2},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2
  61,8,"They seek to extinguish Allah's light (by blowing) with their mouths, but Allah shall spread His light in all its fullness, howsoever the unbelievers may abhor this."{1},footnotes:1:1
  61,9,"He it is Who has sent forth the Messenger with the Guidance and the True Religion that He may make it prevail over all religion, however those that associate aught with Allah in His Divinity might dislike this."{1},footnotes:1:1
  61,10,"Believers, shall I direct you to a commerce that will deliver you from a grievous chastisement?"{1},footnotes:1:1